title: Billion World Invasion
description: Billion World Invasion The Dao of Heaven has collapsed, and the age of domination has come. Cultivator Chen Qiuran accidentally tied the badly damaged Heavenly Dao system and also signed a contract to refine the Heavenly Dao spiritual energy. It is a tale in which an idle social animal becomes an evil demon under the temptation of eight insurers and three golds, and attacks (crosses) billions of worlds. Yi Jie Ruqin 亿界入侵
